Package: riboFootprintR
Type: Package
Title: Fast data extraction and visualization from .bam files for ribosome footprint profiling experiments
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alper Celik
Maintainer: Alper Celik <alpergithub@gmail.com>
Description: Load, process and analyze ribosome footpring profiling data. This packages allows fast and low memory analysis of sorted and indexed .bam files. The package relies on the Samtools C libraries for initial processing so make sure that they are installed and are in PATH.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: GenomicAlignments, ggplot2, plyr, dplyr, zoo, GenomicFeatures, reshape2, rlist
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
